  "time_ut": 1658916773,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dd0\u0db4\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0db8 \u0db8\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dda \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0da7 \u0d89\u0da7\u0dd2\u0db4\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0db8\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "When the electricity was cut off, candles helped to work at Medirigiriya Hospital",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Hospital sources say that the work of the hospital has been severely hampered due to power outages due to non-supply of electricity to the Madirigiriya Base Hospital.",
        "During power outages, we could see how the hospital works were carried out by the light of candles and cell phones.",
        "The hospital staff has arranged to transfer emergency patients, respiratory patients and other patients who require emergency treatment to the Polonnaruwa General Hospital.",
        "A hospital official also said that life-saving equipment stops functioning when the electricity is cut off, and many medicines and pharmaceutical equipment, including medicines that must be stored at different temperatures, are affected.",
        "According to Rohal sources, the electricity generator of Medirigiriya Base Hospital needs about 25 liters of fuel per hour and with the power cut for about three hours on these days, about 75 liters of fuel is needed per day."
      ],
